                <h2><span class="icon data-icon"></span>Information We Collect</h2>
                
                <h3>Information You Provide to Us</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Game Progress:</strong> We store your game progress, scores, achievements, and unlocked levels locally on your device</li>
                    <li><strong>Feedback:</strong> If you contact us for support or provide feedback, we may collect your email address and correspondence</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system version, unique device identifiers</li>
                    <li><strong>Game Analytics:</strong> Gameplay statistics, levels completed, time spent playing</li>
                    <li><strong>Performance Data:</strong> Crash reports, performance metrics to improve game functionality</li>
                    <li><strong>Advertising ID:</strong> If you choose to watch rewarded videos, we may access your device's advertising identifier</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="highlight">
                    <h3>Information We Do NOT Collect</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Personal Identifiable Information:</strong> We do not collect names, addresses, phone numbers, or email addresses unless you voluntarily provide them for support</li>
                        <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> We do not collect or access your precise location</li>
                        <li><strong>Financial Information:</strong> We do not collect payment information (all transactions are handled by app store platforms)</li>
                        <li><strong>Photos/Videos:</strong> We do not access your camera, photos, or videos</li>
                        <li><strong>Contacts:</strong> We do not access your address book or contact list</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2><span class="icon data-icon"></span>How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Game Functionality:</strong> To provide and maintain the game's core features</li>
                    <li><strong>Progress Tracking:</strong> To save and restore your game progress</li>
                    <li><strong>Improvement:</strong> To analyze game performance and improve user experience</li>
                    <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> To respond to your inquiries and provide assistance</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To understand game usage patterns and optimize gameplay</li>
                    <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> To serve relevant ads if you choose to watch rewarded videos</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2><span class="icon security-icon"></span>Data Storage and Security</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Most game data is stored locally on your device</li>
                    <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All data transmissions use industry-standard encryption</li>
                    <li><strong>Security Measures:</strong> We implement reasonable security measures to protect against unauthorized access</li>
                    <li><strong>Data Retention:</strong> We retain game data only as long as necessary to provide the service</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2><span class="icon data-icon"></span>Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>We may use the following third-party services:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Analytics Providers:</strong> To understand game usage (data is anonymized)</li>
                    <li><strong>Ad Networks:</strong> To serve rewarded video ads (only if you choose to watch them)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>These third parties are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information and are prohibited from using it for any purpose other than providing services to us.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2><span class="icon privacy-icon"></span>Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>Our game is suitable for all ages and complies with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA):</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>No Age Gate Required:</strong> We do not collect personal information that would require parental consent</li>
                    <li><strong>Educational Content:</strong> The game focuses on vocabulary building and educational value</li>
                    <li><strong>Safe Environment:</strong> We provide a safe, ad-appropriate environment for children</li>
                    <li><strong>Parental Controls:</strong> Parents can contact us to request deletion of any inadvertently collected information</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

