                    <li><strong>Correction:</strong> You can request correction of inaccurate information</li>
                    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> You can request deletion of your game data</li>
                    <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> You can opt-out of analytics collection in game settings</li>
                    <li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> You can request a copy of your game data</li>
